"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641021164,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"1HCssEp9V8UuWisqpufkJIE1BwJPCHJlse231-3iZ6o\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x5bbDa95e9BC31F9e4cacFF739FC9BE209F456325\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"su1PZmHHxoj-0e4jjzQyVrTmNLcbUH1VdVjvDQc0Nrw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"x-iJFHo1Mqdm9PSx81E5yrKnLvxEOeq8DZKOrDP_HVI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"FJGRc6UNblzz9NgLH8B_0YK0U4wj-d1Qg22IFcGS2D-qix04s3xU7zBMVnRhbi6v2UTvVcr8ikHpEO-aaumv-Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1edd0f6f8db00e8bca8d4cd7e5284c400bbad15e016d64725da07c6a0502a117139f682e7ff897cc03a971296a95531ea07f0e5c0621513bbae824cf965765031b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"su1PZmHHxoj-0e4jjzQyVrTmNLcbUH1VdVjvDQc0Nrw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"x-iJFHo1Mqdm9PSx81E5yrKnLvxEOeq8DZKOrDP_HVI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi